00:33:23.280 --> 00:33:25.044
You get on home now. you hear?

496
00:33:26.404 --> 00:33:28.117
You got church tomorrow.

497
00:33:29.007 --> 00:33:34.861
and we don't want you to be late
for the Lord on our account. you hear?

498
00:33:40.517 --> 00:33:41.995
Sister Virginia?

499
00:33:42.489 --> 00:33:44.541
Hello Reverend. how are you?

500
00:33:44.696 --> 00:33:46.423
I'm doing just fine.

501
00:33:48.668 --> 00:33:50.023
How did you like the service?

502
00:33:50.160 --> 00:33:51.171
Well. I loved it.

503
00:33:51.261 --> 00:33:52.823
If you didn't. would you tell me?

504
00:33:52.941 --> 00:33:54.155
No. Reverend.

505
00:33:54.404 --> 00:33:58.395
I know. I know. if anybody
was going to tell me. it would be you.

506
00:33:58.936 --> 00:34:02.710
Yes. you got to trust and believe
what God tells you.

507
00:34:02.800 --> 00:34:03.844
Yes.

508
00:34:03.929 --> 00:34:05.844
I've been meaning to ask you something--

509
00:34:06.588 --> 00:34:08.320
Come on now.
that's what I've been waiting for.

510
00:34:08.418 --> 00:34:09.444
Come on now.

511
00:34:09.557 --> 00:34:11.360
[laughs] No now. Sister Virginia.

512
00:34:11.811 --> 00:34:13.976
you know we practice
that non-violence over here.

513
00:34:14.602 --> 00:34:15.350
[laughs]

514
00:34:15.444 --> 00:34:17.120
My apologies. Reverend.

515
00:34:17.595 --> 00:34:19.854
You know God is still working on me.

516
00:34:20.230 --> 00:34:23.322
I must say. [?] beginning
where we're at sometimes--

517
00:34:23.440 --> 00:34:26.776
No worries. but I have to ask you.

518
00:34:27.378 --> 00:34:31.157
why do you keep your fist balled up
for the entire service?

519
00:34:33.124 --> 00:34:35.105
Oh. you caught that. huh?

520
00:34:36.028 --> 00:34:37.388
Every Sunday.

521
00:34:37.496 --> 00:34:41.185
Whether my father's preaching.
or if I finally get the chance to preach.

522
00:34:41.967 --> 00:34:46.621
I can see from the pulpit to the back door
you rubbing your knuckles together.

523
00:34:47.077 --> 00:34:50.861
Well. Reverend do you want
the 'we're still in the sanctuary answer'

524
00:34:50.950 --> 00:34:52.616
or do you want me
to give you my answer?

525
00:34:52.720 --> 00:34:54.315
Because I can tell you--

526
00:34:54.550 --> 00:34:57.049
Never mind. never mind.

527
00:34:57.962 --> 00:35:00.856
[sighs] I just thought it was funny.

528
00:35:03.129 --> 00:35:05.011
I love you. Sister Virginia.

529
00:35:06.169 --> 00:35:09.435
I love you too. Reverend.
but before you go.

530
00:35:10.409 --> 00:35:13.463
I have something on my spirit
and I need to get it off.

531
00:35:13.924 --> 00:35:20.080
I'm just not doing too good
with this non-violent stuff. Reverend.

532
00:35:20.207 --> 00:35:25.618
The church [?] and I just feel like

533
00:35:28.240 --> 00:35:30.795
all I know how to do
is use these to fight.

534
00:35:31.270 --> 00:35:33.882
I've been fighting off men my whole life.

535
00:35:34.804 --> 00:35:37.581
I really don't think
I'd want to be out there

536
00:35:37.821 --> 00:35:39.675
with this non-violent protest.

537
00:35:39.750 --> 00:35:41.783
I'm no good.
I shouldn't be out there.

538
00:35:45.397 --> 00:35:46.550
I see.

539
00:35:47.557 --> 00:35:49.284
Well. do you have a license?

540
00:35:50.004 --> 00:35:51.623
No sir. I don't.

541
00:35:52.282 --> 00:35:54.023
Well. I'm going to have to scratch that.

542
00:35:54.310 --> 00:35:56.917
I just figured
if was going to get into a tussle.

543
00:35:57.741 --> 00:36:02.211
maybe you could drive the getaway car.
but you ain't got no license.

544
00:36:02.710 --> 00:36:04.400
[laughs]

545
00:36:04.541 --> 00:36:07.063
Now. look here. Reverend.
I ain't got no license.

546
00:36:07.312 --> 00:36:10.230
but ain't said nothing
about I don't know how to drive.

547
00:36:10.329 --> 00:36:12.531
Now. I can do that.

548
00:36:14.508 --> 00:36:16.352
Pastor. can I bend your ear
for a second?

549
00:36:16.541 --> 00:36:18.381
Yes. talk to me.

550
00:36:18.804 --> 00:36:20.611
Is there somewhere
we can talk in private?

551
00:36:20.705 --> 00:36:24.240
If this can wait about two hours.
we can use my study office.

552
00:36:24.385 --> 00:36:27.115
Because right now. I have a meeting
with some of the core leaders

553
00:36:27.280 --> 00:36:29.510
and leaders of the NAACP.

554
00:36:29.750 --> 00:36:33.581
I got to leave in about 20 minutes.
so I guess we can do our talk here.

555
00:36:36.941 --> 00:36:40.390
I think you want to seriously consider
getting rid of Russ.

556
00:36:41.312 --> 00:36:44.254
Deacon Clyde. not this again.

557
00:36:45.538 --> 00:36:47.171
Look. let me go and get--

558
00:36:47.364 --> 00:36:50.720
Pastor. you're talking
about losing everything. life or death.

559
00:36:50.823 --> 00:36:52.814
Losing everything we've built so far.

560
00:36:55.030 --> 00:36:59.087
Look. me and you
have been to the sandbox.

561
00:36:59.501 --> 00:37:03.190
so I'm going to say it again.
Russ is a good man.

562
00:37:03.435 --> 00:37:05.444
Russ is a gay man.

563
00:37:06.112 --> 00:37:09.369
What he's all about
is going to destroy the movement.

564
00:37:09.468 --> 00:37:10.762
and you know that.

565
00:37:10.912 --> 00:37:14.423
His sissy lifestyle is not conducive
to what we are trying to accomplish.

566
00:37:14.508 --> 00:37:16.560
I'm not going to debate this
with you. my brother.

567
00:37:16.710 --> 00:37:20.108
All the things that you were involved in
and that you left behind.

568
00:37:20.291 --> 00:37:22.960
no man or woman can walk
into this church leadership building

569
00:37:23.049 --> 00:37:25.162
and tell me to cut you off
because of it.

570
00:37:25.369 --> 00:37:27.317
What do you think
they're here to tell you?

571
00:37:27.468 --> 00:37:30.183
What do you think
they're going to say in that meeting?

572
00:37:30.522 --> 00:37:32.183
Like I said--

573
00:37:33.736 --> 00:37:38.150
That the man got caught
with his pants down. literally.

574
00:37:38.729 --> 00:37:41.929
He got caught having sex in a car
with another man.

575
00:37:42.018 --> 00:37:43.901
and a white man at that.

576
00:37:44.338 --> 00:37:47.731
that you have got to get rid of him.
cut him loose.

577
00:37:48.056 --> 00:37:51.477
That arrest warrant he's got.
it's not going to go anywhere.

578
00:37:51.694 --> 00:37:56.715
He committed a lewd act.
got sentenced to 60 days in jail.

579
00:37:57.369 --> 00:38:01.171
and now is a registered sex offender
in the State of California.

580
00:38:02.672 --> 00:38:08.804
[sighs] Russ was our chief organizer
for the March on Washington.

581
00:38:09.830 --> 00:38:12.536
Montgomery was practically all him.

582
00:38:14.955 --> 00:38:19.760
[sighs] He introduced me
to the non-violent teachings of Gandhi.

583
00:38:20.254 --> 00:38:23.322
and now they want me
to end my friendship with him

584
00:38:23.472 --> 00:38:24.917
just because he chooses to--

585
00:38:25.011 --> 00:38:28.809
Look. either you could exile him
[?] of your friendship.

586
00:38:29.176 --> 00:38:32.230
or do nothing
and get exiled along with him.

587
00:38:32.512 --> 00:38:36.211
Because believe me. this movement
will go on without him.

588
00:38:36.512 --> 00:38:38.390
and if necessary. without you.

589
00:38:43.736 --> 00:38:45.510
Is this what they're whispering?

590
00:38:45.877 --> 00:38:47.435
It's no whispering.

591
00:38:47.802 --> 00:38:51.331
Please keep your personal dislikes
for him out of this.

592
00:38:51.482 --> 00:38:56.512
He has done all he can.
you just got to get rid of him now.

593
00:38:56.992 --> 00:38:59.802
If not. you can't blame anybody
but yourself

594
00:38:59.887 --> 00:39:01.425
when it all goes downhill.

595
00:39:02.000 --> 00:39:04.437
I can clearly see
where you stand on this.

596
00:39:04.658 --> 00:39:06.795
and whose side of this that you're on.

597
00:39:07.397 --> 00:39:12.263
I stand on the outside.
outside of a burning house.

598
00:39:14.583 --> 00:39:17.901
You have a good meeting.
peace be with you.

599
00:39:26.329 --> 00:39:29.802
You got one shot.
and one shot only to get this right.

600
00:39:29.905 --> 00:39:32.931
Excuse me.
but I do believe you called me.

601
00:39:33.115 --> 00:39:36.527
and from what you were told.
this is not [?]

602
00:39:36.621 --> 00:39:39.058
This ain't like no entrapment
that you've ever done before.

603
00:39:39.138 --> 00:39:40.550
You got my money?

604
00:39:40.677 --> 00:39:42.080
Slow your ass down.

605
00:39:42.423 --> 00:39:45.590
This money comes with instructions
and consequences.

606
00:39:46.324 --> 00:39:49.477
I usually don't work
with people I don't know. so--

607
00:39:49.651 --> 00:39:53.289
You reached out to a mutual associate.
and they reached out to me.

608
00:39:53.407 --> 00:39:58.225
so apparently. they trust you.
and without a question trust me.

609
00:39:58.936 --> 00:40:01.628
The less I need to know about you.
the better.

610
00:40:02.738 --> 00:40:05.157
I trust that they told you that.
if you do this.

611
00:40:05.407 --> 00:40:08.884
your life as you know it
will never be the same again.

612
00:40:09.011 --> 00:40:12.428
Look. I was told that you needed
a woman like me

613
00:40:12.950 --> 00:40:14.762
to get close to Doctor King

614
00:40:15.369 --> 00:40:18.672
and see if he was even interested
in taking payments.

615
00:40:18.809 --> 00:40:22.320
First off. I'm going to need you
to hold up on that Doctor King shit.

616
00:40:22.828 --> 00:40:25.430
I need someone that can sleep with.
or frame.

617
00:40:25.618 --> 00:40:28.663
or even go public
about Martin Luther King Jr.

618
00:40:29.515 --> 00:40:30.842
Wait. you want me to--?

619
00:40:30.955 --> 00:40:32.550
Sleep with Martin Luther.

620
00:40:33.600 --> 00:40:34.743
I don't know if I--

621
00:40:34.823 --> 00:40:35.910
Need this money?

622
00:40:36.183 --> 00:40:39.454
No. to even be a part of this mess.

623
00:40:40.376 --> 00:40:42.310
This shit you got going ain't right.

624
00:40:43.016 --> 00:40:44.560
Well. it may be too late now

625
00:40:45.021 --> 00:40:47.392
because you know way more
than you need to.

626
00:40:50.070 --> 00:40:51.952
You're the trouble
that I've been looking for.

627
00:40:52.197 --> 00:40:54.136
Number two. Mr. Nat.

628
00:40:56.371 --> 00:40:58.235
Excuse me. miss.
Can you give us a second?

629
00:40:58.343 --> 00:41:00.122
I need just a minute of his life.

630
00:41:01.209 --> 00:41:03.058
This will only take a few minutes.

631
00:41:04.320 --> 00:41:06.705
Don't tiptoe too far now. Miss Sophia.

632
00:41:08.131 --> 00:41:10.475
Now I don't know
what kind of colored man are you

633
00:41:10.597 --> 00:41:11.308
but you got a lot-

634
00:41:11.374 --> 00:41:12.809
Let me stop you right there. Pastor.

635
00:41:12.880 --> 00:41:16.541
No. you can't stop me nowhere
or the God I serve.

636
00:41:17.364 --> 00:41:20.701
You're the devil reincarnated.

637
00:41:20.856 --> 00:41:22.588
Nothing but pure evil.

638
00:41:22.903 --> 00:41:24.607
I heard about you.

639
00:41:24.842 --> 00:41:30.611
Yes. white man got you on a payroll
to destroy the MIA and the SCLC.

640
00:41:30.847 --> 00:41:33.101
Well. you better pray a little harder.

641
00:41:33.637 --> 00:41:38.178
My assignment is
way. way. way more than that.

642
00:41:39.030 --> 00:41:40.164
God don't like this.

643
00:41:40.291 --> 00:41:43.021
Motherfucking God don't like me.

644
00:41:48.767 --> 00:41:50.362
Stay away from us.

645
00:41:50.795 --> 00:41:52.635
We out here preaching the good word.

646
00:41:52.757 --> 00:41:55.308
trying to put in a good fight
for good honest black folk.

647
00:41:55.397 --> 00:41:56.729
News flash.

648
00:41:57.355 --> 00:41:59.491
I'm not the only one that's coming.

649
00:41:59.882 --> 00:42:00.978
You know what?

650
00:42:01.181 --> 00:42:05.341
Everybody has a dash
between their birth and their death

651
00:42:05.670 --> 00:42:10.705
and. if it does your heart any good.
I'll preach your funeral for free.

652
00:42:12.856 --> 00:42:14.880
You do that. motherfucker.

653
00:42:15.134 --> 00:42:16.710
Get out of here.

654
00:42:18.640 --> 00:42:21.920
Sophia. you want this money or what?

655
00:42:26.517 --> 00:42:28.658
Excuse me. Miss Lorraine?

656
00:42:28.870 --> 00:42:30.287
Lorraine. it is. right?

657
00:42:30.418 --> 00:42:35.402
Yes. it is Lady Lorraine but I do believe
you know my name already.

658
00:42:37.270 --> 00:42:38.800
Hot to trot.

659
00:42:39.256 --> 00:42:41.115
I was just making sure.

660
00:42:41.665 --> 00:42:43.195
How can I help you this evening?

661
00:42:43.576 --> 00:42:50.230
You can help all of us by staying out
of Dr. King's face so much.

662
00:42:51.482 --> 00:42:53.472
[?] that would help.

663
00:42:53.717 --> 00:42:55.788
So you know my name

664
00:42:55.868 --> 00:42:59.327
but you don't know
that I'm actually his assistant.

665
00:42:59.425 --> 00:43:01.280
Well. we think that--

666
00:43:01.402 --> 00:43:02.404
We?

667
00:43:04.112 --> 00:43:05.901
Where's the rest of we at?

668
00:43:06.334 --> 00:43:09.392
Didn't the Bible say
all my accusers should be present?

669
00:43:09.548 --> 00:43:12.343
The Bible also speaks about the wicked

670
00:43:12.672 --> 00:43:15.054
and the manner in which
they carry themselves.

671
00:43:15.345 --> 00:43:16.729
Let me reel you back in.

672
00:43:16.818 --> 00:43:19.581
It says that the wicked are amongst us.

673
00:43:21.044 --> 00:43:25.308
How many times have you denied [?]?

674
00:43:25.520 --> 00:43:33.990
You see that's where we go wrong
when we look at a man of God as God.

675
00:43:35.087 --> 00:43:39.863
Now I love my reverends
but I'm not in love with neither of them.

676
00:43:40.894 --> 00:43:43.190
You can kindly take that information

677
00:43:43.440 --> 00:43:47.312
and update whoever it is
that you need to inform.

678
00:43:47.835 --> 00:43:49.562
You see I don't take notes.

679
00:43:50.065 --> 00:43:52.945
That's one of the things that you do

680
00:43:53.129 --> 00:43:56.207
and I know it's going to be hard
for you to keep your legs closed

681
00:43:56.296 --> 00:44:00.592
when you're straddling both sides
of the fence but you go on.

682
00:44:01.181 --> 00:44:03.157
You go on now and play your part.

683
00:44:03.298 --> 00:44:05.849
If I didn't have
something more pressing to do--

684
00:44:05.971 --> 00:44:08.734
Like finishing your itinerary?

685
00:44:08.894 --> 00:44:10.484
I'll get you straight.

686
00:44:10.884 --> 00:44:12.112
Go on now.

687
00:44:12.207 --> 00:44:13.204
Scoot.

688
00:44:13.308 --> 00:44:17.684
[chuckles] I know you've got
to make sure that the people believe

689
00:44:17.788 --> 00:44:20.682
that the poor peoples' march
is still going on.

690
00:44:23.397 --> 00:44:26.282
I'm sure that folks are going to have

691
00:44:26.390 --> 00:44:30.042
a lot of good things
to say about you. Sister Florence.

692
00:44:30.362 --> 00:44:33.115
but the sad part is. and it really is sad.

693
00:44:33.807 --> 00:44:39.087
that you're going to have to die first
before anyone could hear about it.

694
00:44:39.538 --> 00:44:41.204
Well. look at that.

695
00:44:42.955 --> 00:44:45.661
You know you sound just like him now?

696
00:44:46.437 --> 00:44:49.369
I'm not talking about Reverend King.

697
00:44:50.047 --> 00:44:55.369
I'm talking about your half-Asian [?]

698
00:45:06.748 --> 00:45:09.176
It's 3:06 PM. cousin Virginia.

699
00:45:09.792 --> 00:45:11.722
I'm fixing to get ready for work.

700
00:45:12.207 --> 00:45:16.475
Mr. Walters and Mrs. Laurie
don't play about people being late.

701
00:45:16.672 --> 00:45:21.115
Child. I ran to get you on the phone. Ellen.
and now you want to go running.

702
00:45:21.797 --> 00:45:28.197
I'm running because Mr. King. your pastor.
and his guys are here.

703
00:45:28.447 --> 00:45:30.649
Child. I see the pastor all the time.

704
00:45:31.030 --> 00:45:33.082
Now what you need to do is call me

705
00:45:33.167 --> 00:45:37.609
when that there Isaac Hayes comes
[?] a night or two at the motel job.

706
00:45:38.056 --> 00:45:40.828
I fed Mr. King and them last night.

707
00:45:42.240 --> 00:45:44.569
All they ever order is hamburgers.

708
00:45:45.783 --> 00:45:47.308
What I don't understand

709
00:45:47.444 --> 00:45:50.221
is why they don't have
better security where they are.

710
00:45:50.400 --> 00:45:52.917
I don't understand that either.

711
00:45:53.171 --> 00:45:57.157
That FBI. they'll watch him.
they'll follow him.

712
00:45:57.298 --> 00:46:00.315
but they don't put no effort
into trying to protect him.

713
00:46:00.658 --> 00:46:04.790
I'm pretty sure the whole town knows
where he's laying his head at.

714
00:46:05.091 --> 00:46:08.931
People come to that hotel all the time
to get a glimpse of him.

715
00:46:10.056 --> 00:46:13.195
I just don't understand
why he came back here

716
00:46:13.275 --> 00:46:15.190
for the sanitation stuff again.

717
00:46:15.312 --> 00:46:19.976
I'm telling you there's this group
that came to town called the Invaders.

718
00:46:20.414 --> 00:46:25.002
They intentionally made
that march violent last month.

719
00:46:26.122 --> 00:46:30.536
Pastor is bent on making
things peaceful this time around.

720
00:46:31.134 --> 00:46:33.628
Cousin. that man is stressed.

721
00:46:35.407 --> 00:46:37.647
Goes out on the balcony smoking.

722
00:46:38.880 --> 00:46:41.952
Parking lot floor
full of cigarette butts.

723
00:46:43.251 --> 00:46:44.710
Then go back into the room

724
00:46:44.814 --> 00:46:48.517
and all you hear
is grown men pillow fighting.

725
00:46:48.847 --> 00:46:50.051
Child. you know what?

726
00:46:50.136 --> 00:46:53.190
I just pray that they make it home.

727
00:46:53.312 --> 00:46:55.242
They all make it home safe.

728
00:46:55.571 --> 00:46:56.842
I really. really do.

729
00:46:56.941 --> 00:47:00.075
I feel something in my spirit. though.
I got to tell you.

730
00:47:00.263 --> 00:47:04.004
I really. really think
that the last time he was there.

731
00:47:04.112 --> 00:47:07.600
there was nothing but a dry run
as to how they was going to set him up.

732
00:47:07.700 --> 00:47:10.767
I'm telling you.
I just feel it in my spirit. girl.

733
00:47:11.280 --> 00:47:14.828
Virginia. I don't want to be
no eye witness to history

734
00:47:16.207 --> 00:47:19.303
so I just work
and keep my mouth shut.

735
00:47:20.418 --> 00:47:23.543
Every time I mention to our boss.

736
00:47:23.665 --> 00:47:25.585
the black couple that owns the hotel.

737
00:47:25.863 --> 00:47:30.310
that Mr. King should probably be
